    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT280-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">kaḻaṟṟetirmaṟai. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Refusal against [the friend's] urging. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT280">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> kēḷir vāḻiyō kēḷir nāḷumeṉ</l>
          <l> ṉeñcupiṇik koṇṭa vañci lōtip</l>
          <l> peruntōṭ kuṟumakaḷ ciṟumel lāka</l>
          <l> morunāḷ puṇarap puṇari</l>
          <l> ṉaraināḷ vāḻkkaiyum vēṇṭalaṉ yāṉē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>Friends, may you live! Friends,</l>
          <l>if I can only unite for one day</l>
          <l rend="indent2">with the small soft bosom of the little woman with big shoulders</l>
          <l rend="indent2">[and] pretty, few hair, who has laid my heart in fetters</l>
          <l rend="indent8">throughout the days,</l>
          <l>I won't need to live for [another] half day.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
